%% A2A Protocol Communication Flow
%% Shows how RemoteA2aAgent communicates with A2A servers

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as 🎬 Creative Director<br/>(Orchestrator)
    participant AgentTool as 🔧 AgentTool<br/>(Wrapper)
    participant A2AClient as 📡 RemoteA2aAgent<br/>(A2A Client)
    participant Network as 🌐 HTTPS
    participant A2AServer as 🖥️ A2A Server<br/>(Cloud Run)
    participant Agent as 🤖 Specialist Agent<br/>(LlmAgent)
    participant Gemini as ✨ Gemini 2.5 Flash

    Note over Orchestrator: LLM decides to call agent

    Orchestrator->>AgentTool: Function Call:<br/>brand_strategist(query="Research eco bottles")

    AgentTool->>A2AClient: Wrap as A2A request

    Note over A2AClient: Build JSONRPC 2.0 message

    A2AClient->>Network: POST https://service.run.app/<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>{"jsonrpc": "2.0", "method": "agent/invoke"...}

    Network->>A2AServer: HTTPS Request

    Note over A2AServer: Parse JSONRPC<br/>Extract prompt

    A2AServer->>Agent: Execute agent with prompt

    Agent->>Gemini: LLM Call<br/>(System instruction + user prompt)

    Note over Gemini: Generate response<br/>May use tools (google_search)

    Gemini->>Agent: Generated content

    Agent->>A2AServer: Agent output

    Note over A2AServer: Build JSONRPC response

    A2AServer->>Network: HTTP 200 OK<br/>{"jsonrpc": "2.0", "result": {"content": "..."}}

    Network->>A2AClient: HTTPS Response

    A2AClient->>AgentTool: Parse response<br/>Extract content

    AgentTool->>Orchestrator: Return as function result

    Note over Orchestrator: Verify success<br/>Continue to next agent

    rect rgb(52, 168, 83)
    Note over Orchestrator,Gemini: ✅ A2A Protocol Benefits:<br/>• Stateless communication<br/>• Standard JSONRPC format<br/>• Agent cards for discovery<br/>• Works over HTTPS<br/>• Language-agnostic
    end
